GARCIA, A/K/A RICO GARCIA AND LOUIS LUISITO, DEFENDANT.

C-181 Sept.Tern 2017

079161 October 20, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-1993/2903/5473-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
